This folder contains the script files with SNI MLB01 board for the next items of "Embedded Host High Speed Electrical Test Procedure for Embedded host compliance.

1) PID(0x0102) : TEST_J
2) PID(0x0103) : TEST_K
3) PID(0x0101) : TEST_SE0_NAK
4) PID(0x0104) : TEST_PACKET

How to Use
----------
- set CONFIG_DYNAMIC_DEBUG=y at kernel configuration such as milbeaut_p3_tiny_defconfig(*1).
  (*1) This file is sample. please chose your right kernel configuration file in your system.

- build new kernel and burn to rom and boot it

- [xhci case]
    If you want to test with xhci host connected to 2.0 device(*2), call the script file "cn9hdc_host.sh".
    (*2) xhci host connected to 3.0 device is not supported.
    
  [ehci case]
    If you want to test with ehci host, call the script file "cn10hdc_host.sh".

- you can select pattern 1)~4) from menu.

Remarks
-------
- If you want to test other pattern of Electrical test such as next items,
  -- SINGLE SETP GET DEV DESC
  -- SINGLE SETP SET FEATURE
  you should CONFIG_USB_EHSET_TEST_FIXTURE=y at kernel configuration.

